N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 161.11 - Fees

State Regulations

Unless otherwise prescribed by statute, there shall be no
fee charged for: (a) inspection of
records; (b) search for records; or
(c) copies of records. Notes
